- ) Patch

Apply this code to your admin.php file:

if ( !empty($HTTP_GET_VARS['admin']) ) {
	die("Shit! Mantra wins =)");
}

if ( !empty($HTTP_POST_VARS['admin']) ) {
	die("Shit! Mantra wins =)");
}

